hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Through friends digital ebook restore lost hair + 60 day Yes, there’s a direct connection. At one of my Spark & Hustle conferences for women business owners, Stella & Dot founder Jessica Herrin said she’s not at her mental best when she’s not at her physical best. That resonated so strongly with me. There were times I skipped out on key networking events because I worried I didn’t have anything to wear. I didn’t always use my voice because I lacked the confidence to speak out. Confidence that was missing because I didn’t feel my best.
